# Caruso Service Manager — Cursor Rules (V1)

## V1 Scope
- Web app only (no PWA polish yet)
- Stability > refactors
- Shipping focus

## Non-negotiables
- accountId scoping on all backend queries
- Single financial truth (paid / partial / due)
- No duplicate financial logic
- If UI + backend disagree, backend truth wins

## Repo structure (do not invent)
- backend/src/routes
- backend/src/models
- backend/src/utils
- frontend/src/pages
- frontend/src/api
- frontend/src/components
- frontend/src/utils

## Workflow (MANDATORY)
PLAN → PATCH → VERIFY

- PLAN: explain files + approach
- PATCH: minimal diffs only
- VERIFY: how to test + what to watch
- No refactors unless explicitly approved

## Cursor behavior
- Inspection-only unless told otherwise
- Do not modify files during inspection
- List risks before proposing fixes

